,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"旺角太細<br />\n尖沙咀好好多"},{"pid":"4738d494b9d04bfce98d2eba7afef3684702287a","tid":766813,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:19:01.000Z","msg":"係咪全部住港島<br />\n港島人如無必要一定唔過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}